'''S層'''（S-layer, surface layer）是[[古菌|古菌]]和[[細菌|細菌]]{{link-en|細胞包被|cell envelope}}的一部分<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Sára|first=Margit|last2=Sleytr|first2=Uwe B.|date=2000-02-15|title=S-Layer Proteins|url=http://jb.asm.org/content/182/4/859|journal=Journal of Bacteriology|language=en|volume=182|issue=4|pages=859–868|doi=10.1128/JB.182.4.859-868.2000|issn=0021-9193|pmid=10648507|pmc=94357|access-date=2016-10-06|archive-date=2016-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160720223702/http://jb.asm.org/content/182/4/859|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6T9N-44M1F9J-4&_user=10&_origUdi=B7CTD-4SH7GMN-7&_fmt=high&_coverDate=01%2F31%2F2002&_rdoc=1&_orig=article&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=cddfffd5c87e8cc6c0c119e71873cd77 ''S-layers on cell walls of cyanobacteria''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6T9N-44M1F9J-4&_user=10&_origUdi=B7CTD-4SH7GMN-7&_fmt=high&_coverDate=01%2F31%2F2002&_rdoc=1&_orig=article&_acct=C000050221&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=10&md5=cddfffd5c87e8cc6c0c119e71873cd77 |date=20190218011650 }} Micron Volume 33, Issue 3, January 2002, Pages 257–277; {{doi|10.1016/S0968-4328(01)00031-2}}</ref>。S層由[[糖蛋白|糖蛋白]]或[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]鋪成的單分子組成。S層通過分子的自組裝形成，會覆蓋整個細胞表面。因此，S層的蛋白數目可以達到一個細胞蛋白質總數的10%-15%<ref name = "ref1">{{cite journal |vauthors=Messner P, Sleytr U |title=Crystalline bacterial cell-surface layers |journal=Adv. Microb. Physiol. |volume=33 |issue= |pages=213–75 |year=1992 |pmid=1636510 |doi=10.1016/S0065-2911(08)60218-0}}</ref><ref name = "ref2">{{cite journal |vauthors=Pum D, Messner P, Sleytr U |title=Role of the S layer in morphogenesis and cell division of the archaebacterium Methanocorpusculum sinense |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-bacteriology_1991-11_173_21/page/6865 |journal=J. Bacteriol. |volume=173 |issue=21 |pages=6865–73 |year=1991 |pmid=1938891 |pmc=209039}}</ref><ref name = "ref3">{{cite journal |vauthors=Sleytr U, Messner P, Pum D, Sára M |title=Crystalline bacterial cell surface layers |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-microbiology_1993-12_10_5/page/911 |journal=Mol. Microbiol. |volume=10 |issue=5 |pages=911–6 |year=1993 |pmid=7934867 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2958.1993.tb00962.x}}</ref>。S層蛋白在進化上保守性非常低，甚至可以用來分辨親緣關係近的物種。隨物種不同，S層的厚度可從5到25納米不等，且擁有直徑從2納米到8納米不等的孔道<ref name ="ref4">{{cite journal |doi=10.1016/S0168-6445(97)00044-2 |vauthors=Sleytr U, Bayley H, Sára M, Breitwieser A, Küpcü S, Mader C, Weigert S, Unger F, Messner P, Jahn-Schmid B, Schuster B, Pum D, Douglas K, Clark N, Moore J, Winningham T, Levy S, Frithsen I, Pankovc J, Beale P, Gillis H, Choutov D, Martin K |title=Applications of S-layers |journal=FEMS Microbiol. Rev. |volume=20 |issue=1–2 |pages=151–75 |year=1997 |pmid=9276930}}</ref>。

